        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Excellence in Recovery Housing Act</b></p> <p>This bill directs the Substance Abuse and Mental Health Services Administration to promote the availability of high-quality recovery housing for individuals with substance use disorders, including by developing standards and best practices for recovery housing and awarding grants to states, tribes, territories, and localities.</p>]]></text>
